<div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
  <div class="theme-block">
    <div class="rte returns-page-content">
      <div class="enlarge-text">
        <h1>Returns & Exchanges</h1>
        <p>
          At 7Pacific, we truly value you as our customer and appreciate your business. If for any reason you are not
          completely satisfied with your purchase, we're here to make the return process as smooth as possible.
        </p>

        <h2>How to Start a Return</h2>
        <p>
          To initiate a return, simply email us at
          <a href="mailto:returns@7pacificapparel.com">returns@7pacificapparel.com</a> with the following details:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your order number</li>
          <li>The item(s) you would like to return</li>
          <li>The reason for your return</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Once we receive your request, our team will review it and provide you with return instructions.</p>

        <h2>Our Return Policy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Returns are accepted within 30 days of delivery.</li>
          <li>Items must be unused, in original packaging, and in the same condition you received them.</li>
          <li>
            Refunds will be processed back to your original payment method once we have received and inspected the
            returned item(s).
          </li>
          <li>At this time, return shipping costs are the customer's responsibility.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Exchanges</h2>
        <p>
          If you'd like to exchange an item instead of returning it, please let us know in your email. We'll be happy to
          help arrange a replacement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

